          "type": "yny_accordion_group",
          "settings": {
            "item_1_heading": "Key Benefits",
            "item_1_source": "custom",
            "item_1_content": "<ul><li>Helps achieve a soft, silky, shiny and healthy coat</li><li>Support for animals with sensitive skin</li><li>Helps maintain normal moisture content of skin</li><li>May help with occasional or seasonal allergies</li></ul>",
            "item_2_heading": "Key Ingredients",
            "item_2_source": "custom",
            "item_2_content": "<p><strong>Per Chew (2g):</strong></p><ul><li>Linoleic Acid (an Omega 6 Fatty Acid) — 60 mg</li><li>Vitamin E — 25 IU</li><li>Omega 3 Fatty Acids — 20 mg</li><li>Omega 9 Fatty Acids — 26 mg</li></ul>",
            "item_3_heading": "How to Use",
            "item_3_source": "custom",
            "item_3_content": "<p>Give daily based on your dog's weight:</p><ul><li><strong>Up to 25 lbs:</strong> 1 chew per day</li><li><strong>25–50 lbs:</strong> 2 chews per day</li><li><strong>50–75 lbs:</strong> 3 chews per day</li><li><strong>75+ lbs:</strong> 4 chews per day</li></ul><p>Can be given as a treat or crumbled over food. If giving more than 1 chew daily, divide between morning and evening. Store in a cool, dry place.</p>",
            "item_4_heading": "Shipping",
            "item_4_source": "custom",
            "item_4_content": "<p>Free standard shipping on every order — no minimum. Orders are processed within 1 business day and typically arrive within 3–5 business days. Tracking details sent by email once your order ships.</p>",
            "item_5_heading": "",
            "item_5_source": "custom",
